<lb n="0904b02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1383</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0904b03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0904006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說宿命智陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0904b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0904b05" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0904007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（西天…師））十八字＝（（三藏法師））四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0904007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿明教大師）十八字＝（（三藏法師））四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0904007"><lem wit="【大】">西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0904b06" ed="T"/>明教大師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">三藏法師</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">宋西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿明教大師</rdg></app><note n="0904008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔臣〕－【三】</note><note n="0904008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔臣〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0904008"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0904b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0904b0701">爾時世尊告阿難言。有陀羅尼名宿命智。若
<lb n="0904b08" ed="T"/>有眾生聞是陀羅尼。能<note n="0904009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">志＝至【元】【明】</note><app n="0904009"><lem wit="【大】">志</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">至</rdg></app>心受持者。所有千
<lb n="0904b09" ed="T"/>劫之中極重罪業皆悉消<note n="0904010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滅＝除【明】</note><app n="0904010"><lem wit="【大】">滅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">除</rdg></app>。若能終身不間
<lb n="0904b10" ed="T"/>斷者。是人於七俱胝生常知宿命。即說陀羅
<lb n="0904b11" ed="T"/>尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0904b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0904b1201" type="dharani"><note n="0904011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梵字載於卷末</note>那謨<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0904012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【元】【明】</note><app n="0904012"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">羅</rdg></app>怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>室詰泥<note place="inline">去聲呼下同一</note>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;
<lb n="0904b13" ed="T"/>多<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">二</note>阿囉曷<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>三藐訖三<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱
<lb n="0904b14" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline"><app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】【麗】【磧砂】" cf1="K34n1224_p0479b15" cf2="Q33_p0208a17">三</lem><rdg wit="【大】">二</rdg></app></note>怛&CB00853;他<note place="inline">引四</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛泥<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛泥<note place="inline">二合五</note>
<lb n="0904b15" ed="T"/>蘇囉怛泥<note place="inline">二合六</note>囉怛努<note place="inline">二合引</note>訥婆<note place="inline">二合</note>味<note place="inline">引七</note>摩
<lb n="0904b16" ed="T"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>枳囉尼<note place="inline">去聲八</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>三婆
<lb n="0904b17" ed="T"/>味<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引九</note></p>
<lb n="0904b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0904b1801">爾時阿難聞佛宣說。令諸眾生得宿命智陀
<lb n="0904b19" ed="T"/>羅尼已。歎未曾有歡喜無量。即以頭頂禮佛
<lb n="0904b20" ed="T"/>而退。</p>
<lb n="0904b21" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說宿命智陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
